cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.AI, cs.IR 

This paper is about person re-identification, which is a computer vision task. Therefore, cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also proposes a new ensemble network using deep learning methods, which falls under the sub-category of cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper uses datasets and evaluates the performance, which could also fall under cs.MM (Multimedia). The paper also discusses the effectiveness of the proposed method, which could be categorized under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the paper involves similarity computation, which could be categorized under cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
